%% Paste this file into https://mermaid.live to render and export PNG.
%% Save the exported file as assets/architecture.png so it shows up in README.md.

flowchart LR
    User([User CLI Input]) --> InputGuard[Input Validation Guardrail]
    InputGuard -->|invalid| ErrorOut[Friendly Error Message]
    InputGuard -->|valid| Agent[Claude Agent Loop / Mock Planner]

    Agent <-->|retrieve top-k| KB[(RAG Knowledge Base<br/>data/knowledge_base.json)]
    Agent -->|tool_use| Tool[recommend_songs Tool]
    Tool --> Scorer[Weighted Scoring Engine<br/>genre / mood / mood_tags /<br/>energy / danceability /<br/>acousticness / popularity / decade]
    Scorer --> Diversity[Artist Diversity Penalty]
    Diversity --> Ranker[Top-K Ranker]
    Ranker -->|tool_result| Agent

    Agent --> OutGuard[Output Guardrail<br/>Explanation vs Score Consistency]
    OutGuard --> Display[tabulate Output Table]
    Display --> User

    Logger[(logs/agent.log)]
    Agent -.steps.-> Logger
    OutGuard -.flags.-> Logger

    Eval[eval.py Test Harness] -.drives.-> InputGuard
    Eval -.audits.-> OutGuard
    Eval -.reports.-> Report[Pass/Fail Summary Table]
